ISMAIL Platform License Notice

This software is part of the ISMAIL Platform, a comprehensive digital ecosystem
designed for the ECOWAS (Economic Community of West African States) region.

The ISMAIL Platform includes:
- Biometric authentication and KYC services
- Electronic wallet and payment processing
- E-commerce and marketplace functionality
- Hotel booking and reservation systems
- Real estate management tools
- Debt collection and recovery services

